      <title>美联储鲍曼：“尚未”准备好降息，如果需要愿意再次加息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-bowman-not-yet-ready-rate-cuts-willing-hike-again-if-needed-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事米歇尔·鲍曼周四表示，美国经济尚未达到美联储应该降息的地步，尽管通胀下降和最终降息的底线仍然存在，但仍不能排除收紧货币政策的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-bowman-not-yet-ready-rate-cuts-willing-hike-again-if-needed-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 14:13:45 GMT</pubDate>
