      <title>需求萎缩影响销售预期，维多利亚的秘密 (Victoria's Secret) 下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/victorias-secret-falls-shrinking-demand-hits-sales-forecasts-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维多利亚的秘密周四，该内衣品牌预计，由于北美主要市场的消费者转向更便宜的选择，开年低迷，年销售额将下降，该公司股价周四盘前暴跌约 29%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/victorias-secret-falls-shrinking-demand-hits-sales-forecasts-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 14:10:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
