      <title>LinkedIn 罕见地透露，付费订阅带来了 17 亿美元的收入</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/rare-disclosure-linkedin-says-premium-subscriptions-bring-17-billion-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LinkedIn 周四首次披露了其高级订阅业务的销售额，称该部门的收入将在 2023 年达到 17 亿美元，因为该公司看到新人工智能工具的采用有所增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/rare-disclosure-linkedin-says-premium-subscriptions-bring-17-billion-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 14:04:46 GMT</pubDate>
