      <title>欧洲央行下调增长和通胀预测</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-cuts-growth-inflation-projections-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周四下调了部分增长和通胀预期，将明年物价增长目标调整至 2%，原因是经济增长疲软和能源价格良性限制了物价压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-cuts-growth-inflation-projections-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 13:29:10 GMT</pubDate>
