      <title>欧洲央行维持利率不变，但承认通胀有所降温</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-keeps-rates-hold-acknowledges-some-inflation-cooling-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周四如预期维持利率不变，但承认通胀放缓速度比之前预期的要快，这可能为今年晚些时候的降息开辟道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-keeps-rates-hold-acknowledges-some-inflation-cooling-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 13:21:53 GMT</pubDate>
